24_11_11_d544063a66ff94b9c61bg-053.jpg?height=427&width=401&top__y=980&top__x=468","line":1060,"embedded":true},{"title":"|764x188","target":"https://cdn.mathpix.com/cropped/2024_11_11_d544063a66ff94b9c61bg-055.jpg?height=256&width=1043&top__y=1369&top__x=362","line":1091,"embedded":true},{"title":"0, \\frac{\\sqrt{5}}{5}\\.$ )；\n(4) $\\triangle F M N$ 周长的最小值为 $\\sqrt{2}+1$.\n\n其中正确结论的为（）\nA. (1)(2)\nB. (2)(3)\nC. (3)(4)\nD. (1)(4)\n![","target":"https://cdn.mathpix.com/cropped/2024_11_11_d544063a66ff94b9c61bg-078.jpg?height=427&width=404&top__y=980&top__x=466","line":1534},{"title":"2,+\\infty)$\nD. $(-\\infty, 2) \\cup(2,+\\infty)$\n\n#### 10.2.2 【 练 1-1\n\n圆 $x^{2}+y^{2}+4 \\sin \\theta \\cdot x+4 \\cos \\theta \\cdot y+1=0$ 的半径等于 $\\qquad$ .\n\n#### 10.2.3 【 练 1-2\n\n已知 $A(-2,2) ， B(2,6)$ ，则以 $A B$ 为直径的圆的标准方程为 $\\qquad$ .\n\n#### 10.2.4 【 练 1-3\n\n正方形草地 $A B C D$ 边长 $1.2 ， E$ 到 $A B ， A D$ 距离为 $0.2 ， F$ 到 $B C ， C D$ 距离为 0.4 ，有个圆形通道经过 $E ， F$ ，且与 $A D$ 只有一个交点，求圆形通道的周长 $\\qquad$ . (精确到 $0.01)$\n![","target":"https://cdn.mathpix.com/cropped/2024_11_11_d544063a66ff94b9c61bg-118.jpg?height=318&width=304&top__y=889&top__x=299","line":2226},{"title":"                                                             | 201x197","target":"https://cdn.mathpix.com/cropped/2024_11_11_d544063a66ff94b9c61bg-144.jpg?height=197&width=201&top__y=1293&top__x=738","line":2683,"embedded":true},{"title":"                                                             | 212x197","target":"https://cdn.mathpix.com/cropped/2024_11_11_d544063a66ff94b9c61bg-144.jpg?height=197&width=212&top__y=1513&top__x=723","line":2684,"embedded":true},{"title":"                                                             | 201x156","target":"https://cdn.mathpix.com/cropped/2024_11_11_d544063a66ff94b9c61bg-144.jpg?height=156&width=201&top__y=1742&top__x=738","line":2685,"embedded":true},{"title":"|401x429","target":"https://cdn.mathpix.com/cropped/2024_11_11_d544063a66ff94b9c61bg-161.jpg?height=429&width=401&top__y=982&top__x=468","line":3034,"embedded":true},{"title":"50,60$ ) 内的人数为 16 ，则下列结论正确的是（）\n![","target":"https://cdn.mathpix.com/cropped/2024_11_11_d544063a66ff94b9c61bg-185.jpg?height=435&width=618&top__y=1781&top__x=296","line":3503}],"task_lines":[],"tasks":{},"codeblock_ranges":[],"last_embed":{"hash":"1c51oxn","at":1771320380397}},"smart_blocks:09-讲义汇总/XDF讲义/FY25 高三数学秋季【行远班教材】修改版本.md#": {"path":null,"embeddings":{"TaylorAI/bge-micro-v2":{"vec":[-0.07630568,-0.01438455,0.05249466,0.00835513,0.02661044,-0.01233961,-0.03989028,0.00440466,0.03976705,0.08265783,0.022685,-0.07370487,0.05782351,0.00565357,0.00513547,0.00013217,-0.0008043,-0.02680092,-0.05854086,-0.02332585,0.11744903,0.00508694,-0.029832,-0.06024789,0.05188676,0.05277116,-0.01207714,-0.06264041,-0.05497904,-0.19030255,-0.02259475,0.07351863,0.05488578,0.03370808,0.05438891,-0.04883377,-0.03827132,0.07208113,0.00253496,0.06883956,-0.01814072,0.08223218,-0.0146801,-0.00102834,-0.01915405,-0.11178655,-0.01315756,-0.00506125,0.02372807,-0.02576936,0.00143383,-0.04473242,0.0019131,0.03679515,-0.00947099,-0.00398545,0.04778367,0.01493113,0.01732478,0.0032226,0.02234379,0.00635055,-0.2207123,0.04505429,0.05453666,-0.04443828,-0.05630313,-0.06072975,0.00631242,0.05757453,-0.03290195,-0.00233466,-0.00267801,0.00991786,-0.0460352,-0.04499049,-0.01372219,-0.1111191,-0.02315602,-0.06107246,-0.00979823,0.11450662,-0.04849719,-0.00689557,0.00420243,0.03924238,0.01108933,-0.05323334,-0.0045495,-0.02851592,0.00807465,-0.01598711,-0.00728021,0.00133534,-0.0860388,-0.05943553,0.02807294,0.0122608,-0.03285098,0.07804739,-0.03016186,0.01783966,0.02834939,-0.01642155,-0.04409494,0.02642303,-0.00657385,-0.05399637,-0.05116108,-0.02230456,-0.04956084,0.00618662,0.10729168,-0.01167735,-0.02273007,0.01209545,-0.0279755,-0.02369235,-0.01802213,0.0368132,0.01344737,0.01272053,0.02084435,-0.01418072,0.0427349,-0.01583965,-0.00174263,0.00266245,0.02146325,0.04663979,0.04544431,-0.03154086,-0.0146028,-0.01086546,-0.06382243,0.005